meta.description: Simply manage a folder of project-boiler-plates and use the built-in CLI tool to print projects to any folder on your machine. I was inspired by front-end frameworks that provide the same thing, but in a much more restricted way. This solution provides a 100% customizable experience. This is still in maintenance at the moment, but it is very usable already.
meta.title: A simple way to generate customized boiler-plate code
